definition: strong/powerful/better/slightly more than/vigorous/violent/best in their category, e.g. see 百強|百强[bai3 qiang2]
to force/to compel/to strive/to make an effort

sentences.english: High crosslink starch nearly didn't dissolve in boiled water and could sop up more water.
sentences.chinese: 高交联淀粉溶解性能降低，而吸水性能增强。

sentences.english: You'll also strengthen your hip flexors and Achilles tendons.
sentences.chinese: 您还可以增强您的髋屈肌和脚腕筋腱。

sentences.english: CFRP, after all, is 50 times as expensive as steel.
sentences.chinese: 毕竟，碳纤维增强塑料比钢贵50倍。

sentences.english: Only a handful of bridges have major support beams made from them.
sentences.chinese: 只有少数桥梁采用纤维增强塑料的主体支撑梁。

sentences.english: Moreover, subjects' perceptions on safe sex and self-protection from sex risk behavior in the intervention group were improved.
sentences.chinese: 此外，干预组对象的安全性行为和自我保护意识增强。

sentences.english: The effect of real-time water surface can consumedly enhance the immersion characteristic of virtual reality system.
sentences.chinese: 实时水面效果可以大大增强虚拟现实系统的沉浸感。

sentences.english: Along with the extending of time, the contact toxicity of A. wormwood extracts on drosophila increased.
sentences.chinese: 随着时间的延长，艾草提取液对果蝇的触杀效果增强。

sentences.english: Glutaraldehyde can strengthen the conjugation of NCF with protein.
sentences.chinese: 用戊二醛处理硝酸纤维素膜可以增强蛋白吸附。

sentences.english: Doing so strengthens capacities and builds self-reliance.
sentences.chinese: 这样做可以增强能力和实现自力更生。

sentences.english: May potentiate oral anticoagulants, others that prolong bleeding.
sentences.chinese: 口服抗凝血剂，会增强，也有人认为延长出血。

sentences.english: This capability provides foundation for support and enhancement the consumption of enterprise services by others.
sentences.chinese: 这个能力为支持和增强他人消费企业服务提供了基础。

sentences.english: Dead-zone operator is adopted in the adaptive algorithm, which improves the robustness of the algorithm.
sentences.chinese: 自适应算法中采用了死区算子，增强了算法的鲁棒性。

sentences.english: One reason is the increasing upward mobility of the younger generation.
sentences.chinese: 原因之一是年轻一代的上进心增强了。

sentences.english: After tough training, I got rid of my self-abasement and became confident.
sentences.chinese: 经过艰苦的训练，使我增强了自信心，消除了自卑感。

sentences.english: The report noted the need for stronger US-China military ties.
sentences.chinese: 报告指出增强美中军事联系的重要性。

sentences.english: To enhance the development of vocational education service support, training of technical personnel.
sentences.chinese: 要增强职业教育服务发展支撑力，培养技术技能人才。
